{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"d7df9bb60b","title":"报纸一个时期要有一定的方向","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"2f6b26ae74","index":0,"year":1958,"month":9,"day":null,"articleId":"d7df9bb60b"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji40","name":"毛泽东全集第40卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/40-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji40":{"comments":[{"id":"86cfbd9ece","publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"d7df9bb60b","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"本篇是毛泽东和吴冷西谈话的一部分。"},{"id":"a517467976","publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"d7df9bb60b","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"刊于1958年1月8日《人民日报》。"}],"contents":[{"id":"3a481cdef0","type":"title","text":"报纸一个时期要有一定的方向“","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"d7df9bb60b"},{"id":"86cfbd9ece","type":"paragraph","text":"对国际问题应该有研究，有一定的看法，不要临时抱佛脚，发表感想式的意见。对许多国际问题都要有基本的看法，应该有比较深刻的议论。现在对国际问题的意见，有些是感想式的。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"d7df9bb60b"},{"id":"a517467976","type":"paragraph","text":"搞新闻工作，光务实，不务虚，不好。有了看法，有了意见，就要找机会、找题目发挥。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"d7df9bb60b"},{"id":"4e2de652c9","type":"paragraph","text":"报纸宣传，报纸编辑工作，最近一两个月比较杂，看不出方向，究竟搞什么？今年春天，发表《从梅林看全国》的社论时是有方向的。最近一两个月，东西很多，方向不大明了。报纸应该有方向，在最近就要转变过来。省报也应当如此。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"d7df9bb60b"},{"id":"145533953d","type":"paragraph","text":"报纸一个时期要有一定的方向，把大家的注意力集中过来","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"d7df9bb60b"}],"page":{"id":"7b2cab391b","publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"d7df9bb60b","start":276,"end":276}}}},"__N_SSG":true}